description: The Lyxor DJ Global Titans 50 UCITS ETF is a UCITS compliant exchange traded fund that aims to track the benchmark index Dow Jones Global Titans 50 EUR.The Dow Jones Global Titans 50 EUR is a 50-stock index that reflects the market performance of the world’s leading multinational companies. Stocks are selected from the Dow Jones Global Index SM, a broad market benchmark that covers 51 countries. Criteria for DJGT stock selection include float-adjusted market capitalization, sales/revenue and net income. The index is calculated in both U.S. dollars and Euros.Lyxor ETFs are efficient investment vehicles listed on exchange that offer transparent, liquid and low-cost exposure to the underlying benchmark index.
name: Lyxor DJ Global Titans 50 UCITS ETF
